{
  "stem": "10564.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a big mountain and a big hole in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So a lot of times, they took our commander from the Steinbruch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was three, four people they took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we supposed-- we spray special chemicals so there would not be typhus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were covered with a foot of dirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walk on the body.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walk on the body.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cover it with a foot of dirt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We always put the dirt on the side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So with the shovel, we throw inside, from all around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then-- and there was the next people came in, we do the same thing all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I remember one thing now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came in about 50 Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We work here, and the thing was, the whole thing was maybe about 100 feet away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they were tied in completely, like you tied it in, completely tied in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We supposed to carry them from the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put a log this way, six, seven log in that Polish underground, this way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A log and this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We pile up maybe about 6, 7 feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were three or four or five of bunches, you know, of the logs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "German went in and put gas on the top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He took a gun and ignite it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was singing, like we sing, 'Oh Beautiful' here, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were singing [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Screaming, to see this, it's unbelievable thing, human being were burned alive, alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, after thing what happened, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was two, three wheelbarrows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We took the wheelbarrows, throw to the mountain there, throw it like this because there was ashes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The wood was burning for two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
